---
source: crates/daemon/tests/cli_help.rs
expression: stdout
---
Snooze a message until a specified time

Usage: mxr snooze [OPTIONS] --until <UNTIL> [MESSAGE_ID]

Arguments:
  [MESSAGE_ID]  

Options:
      --until <UNTIL>    When to resurface: tomorrow|monday|weekend|tonight|ISO8601
      --search <SEARCH>  
      --yes              
      --dry-run          
  -h, --help             Print help
